<plot>After completing his schooling from Nalanda, Ajay Kumar Saxena returns and is hired as a Teacher. He meets with savvy students, whose names are Jaya, Neelam, Shilpa, Sonam, Chunky, Govinda, with Jaya having a crush on him, and wants to wed him. He, instead, weds Saraswati, from a local orphanage, brings her home, while Jaya leaves the hostel and moves in next door. Jaya's agenda is to befriend Saraswati and thus continue to be near her lover, and she meets this goal with considerable success. When Jaya's dad is killed, Saraswati asks Jaya to move in, bringing chaos to Ajay's life amidst threats from a terrorist named Captain - who will soon hold the school and all it's inhabitants hostage.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?039229</url></doc>
